<div class="text-center">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-500 mb-2">StellArb</h1>
  <p class="text-lime-400 mb-8">Stellar Arbitrage Trading System</p>

  <div class="bg-blue-900 border-2 border-orange-500 p-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">System Access</h2>

    <%= form_with model: @user, url: sessions_path, local: true do |f| %>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <%= f.label :email, "Email Address", class: "block text-sm font-bold mb-2" %>
        <%= f.email_field :email,
            class: "w-full px-3 py-2 bg-blue-950 border border-blue-700 rounded focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none",
            placeholder: "pilot@example.com",
            required: true,
            autofocus: true %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <%= f.submit "Request Access Code",
            class: "w-full bg-orange-500 text-blue-950 font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-orange-400 transition-colors cursor-pointer" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
      <p>A one-time access code will be sent to your email.</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-xs">(Development mode: auto-login enabled)</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 text-xs text-gray-500">
    <p>You are traveling through space.</p>
    <p>It's like a maze of twisty passages that look all alike,</p>
    <p>but that's another game. This game has lasers.</p>
  </div>
</div>